{"tid":1308924,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"長文慎入有圖 去迪士尼之前請三思！！","createTime":"2019-07-12T04:24:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T05:29:02.000Z","uid":188005,"like":24,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1165ebbaeb76f828fa8f9e0ad41c3e606fe9b9f1","tid":1308924,"uid":188005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:24:01.000Z","msg":"表達能力差，同大家Say定Sorry 先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話說小妹前兩日去迪士尼俾人偷電話，係喺其中一間鋪俾人偷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事發經過<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有個大陸佬貼到我勁近，用頂Cap帽遮住隻手同我個褲袋，</span><br />\n我認我ON9完全無為意佢係偷電話，<br />\n淨係想快啲離開間鋪因為又焗又多人抖唔到氣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同行朋友雖然後面全程望到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但都無第一時間諗佢想偷野，<br />\n淨係以為佢係想摸我，我再摸下褲袋部電話已經唔見咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n前後只不過係幾分鐘嘅時間, <br />\n已經9秒9去City Hall 話俾人偷野，仲報埋警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />報警係因為想迪士尼開CCTV俾我地睇，廢時話公司規定無得亂開閉路俾客人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n心諗<span style=\"color: red;\">好似</span>都好大機會搵得返 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個日仲要落狗屎 條友唔會去到D咩地方<br />\n仲要咁好彩我事發經過連條友個特徵我都記得好清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">我：你地可唔可以開CCTV出黎俾我地認下人，你地同事搵人果陣都可以具體知道佢個特徵同外形係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">保安：我地無CCTV架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">我：下咁你地鋪頭天花板上面個D咩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">保安：Umm。。。個啲閉路電視監控範圍淨係影到Cashier</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">我：。。。。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n分唔到佢係講真定假，<br />\n但依加咩年代 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用喺鋪頭入面嘅閉路電視原來淨係睇到一粒米範圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n更何況係一個大型遊樂場入面用嘅閉路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能因為我連警都報埋所以迪士尼D人好驚搞到好大件事所以全程同我地一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後我又無心機再玩所以喺city hall入面間房坐住等消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實再之前我比咗個建議佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>因為迪士尼係一個密閉空間，出口只得一個，而我又完全清楚個賊外型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n所以想佢地搵一個保安同我一齊企出口，因為係一個位置等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好過喺園區入面亂兜<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲要個賊點都要離開迪士尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n跟住佢地即刻ban我話佢地無執法權力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然我都知我只係一個小人物，無可能用咁多人力去幫我搵部電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但洗唔洗講D當人係傻仔嘅說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>本身迪士尼就有責任同盡所能去保障遊客安全同財產</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁有條友喺間鋪入面打完人走甩到就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n迪士尼入面偷野都無人會知同發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n因為個CCTV跟本係廢的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋D職員會以無執法權力去同你講節哀順變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打上黎都係想呻下圍下爐同埋想你地<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">小心身邊可疑大陸佬</span></span>，<br />\n今時香港唔同往日，由細到大都未試過俾人偷野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算漏底咗銀包電話都會有好心人俾返我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n懷疑部電話係俾集團式小偷偷咗，<span style=\"color: red;\">專去迪士尼/海洋公園搵食</span>，多人易得米，因為到依加find my iphone 都無online 過，應該係一批老鼠貨拎去賣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">P.S. 迪士尼Fans但以後都唔會再去香港迪士尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bEu1Vge.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbEu1Vge.jpg&h=d9a10b61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xdWoo9A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxdWoo9A.jpg&h=8e449319&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"18e259e337181963c9df5cb53d1dda65cba86c1d","tid":1308924,"uid":203619,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:27:10.000Z","msg":"自己問題會唔會大過迪士尼呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你果個位比人偷都未必會影到啦"},{"pid":"ae20d7f30fbb966b5d801317f362741eadfbe112","tid":1308924,"uid":196861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:27:23.000Z","msg":"以前係入面翻parttime<br />\n啲大陸人成日用架bb車側側膊偷野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9306e31de12f0e7329e3214e73b19ed692e47d23","tid":1308924,"uid":264457,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:30:56.000Z","msg":"呢件事只能說係不幸，個人財物自己要小心保管，我見唔到佢迪士尼有做錯既地方。"},{"pid":"3a83e4e9ceed119c443bb7c0b5e39344d7f0d88f","tid":1308924,"uid":188005,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"18e259e337181963c9df5cb53d1dda65cba86c1d","tid":1308924,"uid":203619,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:27:10.000Z","msg":"自己問題會唔會大過迪士尼呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你果個位比人偷都未必會影到啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:39:53.000Z","msg":"我係有問題，但個閉路淨係影住cashier有無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3969a1c41a9fff28a0ac11d756fcf44f8eee7c0","tid":1308924,"uid":188005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae20d7f30fbb966b5d801317f362741eadfbe112","tid":1308924,"uid":196861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:27:23.000Z","msg":"以前係入面翻parttime<br />\n啲大陸人成日用架bb車側側膊偷野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:40:54.000Z","msg":"7成都係大陸人，仲要撞黎撞去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f837ca4b98b8837fb5db2d744191ecd64644c55b","tid":1308924,"uid":35031,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:46:09.000Z","msg":"其實會唔會係你邏輯有問題？<br />\n首先<br />\n1. 你無權睇CCTV 就算影到都只可以比警察睇<br />\n2. 保安的確無執法權力、無權唔比人離開、唔比個人走可以被告返禁錮、而且你認錯人咁責任計落邊個到？<br />\n<br />\n所以你其實可以做既係即刻報警 等警察處理 保安係幫唔到你<br />\n不過警察會唔會處理 你睇出面咁多警犬post就知<br />\n<br />\n所以呢個時勢除左自己小心<br />\n就係出黎屌9香港警察冇用<br />\n細case唔做 下下叫人銷案"},{"pid":"bb4bc3befc905d560d49bea7cd96bf464815a16b","tid":1308924,"uid":27432,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:49:51.000Z","msg":"報警都唔會理你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果個賊係示威者都可能會落力啲<br />\n係同胞真係彩你都傻"},{"pid":"e4a0777a6d6ebbb0eaba84c800ac7981bc60c12e","tid":1308924,"uid":11127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:51:30.000Z","msg":"絲打轉去海洋公園"},{"pid":"d9aa1582ccb80af57111